The '''Anthem of Arkhangelsk Oblast''' ({{lang-ru|Гимн Архангельской области}}, ''Gimn Arkhangel'skoy oblasti'') is an anthem used for the [[Arkhangelsk Oblast|Oblast of Arkhangelsk]] in [[Russia]]. The anthem was approved by the Arkhangelsk Regional Assembly on 31 October [[2007 год|2007]]. The author of the lyrics and composer of the music of the anthem is [[Мешко, Нина Константиновна|Nina Konstantinovna Meshko]].

