The '''Cercle de Lorraine''' or '''Club van Lotharingen''' is a [[Belgium|Belgian]] business club, located in [[Brussels]], [[Belgium]]. The club was founded in 1998, and it wants to bring together, distinguished and representative personalities from the Belgian [[financial]] community, French speaking ([[Wallonia]], south part of Belgium) as well as Dutch speaking ([[Flanders]], north part of Belgium), who are united within an honorary committee.
